In the numerical simulation, we mostly focus on the transient dynamics of the model system to see how the integrated model (8) connecting three domains of human population, creates a reinforcing cycle to initiate the development of resistance in population. Figure S6 in SI shows a sample time series explaining how the population density of a highly prevalent commensal (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
